lm.fit1=update(lm.fit, ~.-age)

3.6.4 Interaction Terms

  • The syntax lstat:black tells R to include an interaction term between lstat and black
  • The syntax lstat*age simultaneously includes lstat, age, and the interaction term lstatage as predictors; it is a shorthand for lstat+age+lstat:age.
summary(lm(medv~lstat*age, data=Boston))
